-------------------------------------------------------------------------
logic converter - bi directional - converts 5 V logic to 3.3 V or vice-vesa - multi channel and cheap
-------------------------------------------------------------------------
rplidar is 360 degrees - uses the principle of laser triangulation -  8000 points at 10 Hz - internal wireless connection and no slip rings

-------------------------------------------------------------------------

setup ssh -

installation - sudo apt-get install openssh-server
checking - sudo systemctl status ssh 
connection - ssh username@IPaddress
use ifconfig to get the IP adddress


sudo systemctl start/stop ssh 
sudo systemctl enable/disable ssh - for  operation during startup 

https://linuxize.com/post/how-to-enable-ssh-on-ubuntu-18-04/

